member.example:
This sample shows how to call GetAccountAsync.

Uri endpoint = new Uri("<endpoint>");
TokenCredential credential = new DefaultAzureCredential();
Accounts client = new AuthManagerClient(endpoint, credential).GetAccountsClient(apiVersion: "2024-12-01");

Response<Account> response = await client.GetAccountAsync("sampleAccountId");

